comments.body:
it seems to me that `next` remains unchanged after clear:
```C++
        auto next{node->second.Next()};
        node->second.ClearFlags();
        assert(next == node->second.Next());
        node = next;
```
so if that's intentional, we can simplify to:
```C++
        node->second.ClearFlags();
        node = node->second.Next();
```

